snippet.title: Norwich City Tour 2021
snippet.description:
Welcome to the fine city of Norwich in Norfolk, I'll take you on a tour of the city checking out some beautiful sights along the way and some places you may never have come across!
Highlights include Norwich Market, Norwich Castle, Norwich Theatre Royal, Norwich Cathedral, The Forum, filming locations for movies and tv shows like Elm Hill, The riverside and of course Norwich City Football Club and so much more! Come along on the walk with me!
